    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Start About Section -->
<section class="section bg-blue" id="about-dekkson">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 align-self-center mb-4 mb-md-0 section-welcome">
        <div class="align-self-center">
          <h2 style="margin-bottom: 50px;">Selamat Datang di <span class="title-about-section">Dekkson Loyalty Program</span></h2>
          <p class="txt-white text-welcome-section">Hanya dengan mengirimkan foto struk belanja, kamu bisa mendapatkan point dan menukarnya dengan puluhan rewards sesuka mu!</p>
          <p class="txt-white text-welcome-section">Tunggu apa lagi ? Ayo segera daftar !</p>
          <p class="txt-white" style="margin-top:40px;">Syarat dan ketentuan ? <a href="#">Cek disini</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 ">
        <form class="text-left clearfix bg-white bg-login form-login" action="#">
          <div class="form-group title-login-box">
            <h4 class="title-loginbox">Login Disini !</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group row">
            <label class="col-sm-4 col-form-label">Email / No Telepon</label>
            <div class="col-sm-8">
              <input type="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Email / No Telepon anda" id="email">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group row">
            <label class="col-sm-4 col-form-label">Password</label>
            <div class="col-sm-8">
              <input type="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Password anda" id="password">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group row">
            <div class="col-sm-12">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-main float-right" id="login_btn">Login</button>
            </div>
          </div>
